: https://cash.me/$Lifeprint\nWant to order a USB drive with four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":54,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CL8BEM2rARgBIhMIqMjUi7jrkwMVhKMrBh1-gxMBSKTnrZmFpK65YsoBBP-JbFQ=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbkF5d0o2WjNCb2V4WXE4eXkyd0VQSWVHcm05d3xBQ3Jtc0tuTEdqNUtMZzRLWmNuRTJfVGtoalpOZWt4V1pFa1V6ck9xQ1M1RkdMRi1fakdta3J6amR4bTlGLU4wUXFTajFvRVhhUjgzc2s0ZTBsV0R1bmx3RXMzU1YtMlpudTNDWERSRnYxMXVJQkgwODZ3WWhrVQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=YnK5IFMrc6Q","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbkF5d0o2WjNCb2V4WXE4eXkyd0VQSWVHcm05d3xBQ3Jtc0tuTEdqNUtMZzRLWmNuRTJfVGtoalpOZWt4V1pFa1V6ck9xQ1M1RkdMRi1fakdta3J6amR4bTlGLU4wUXFTajFvRVhhUjgzc2s0ZTBsV0R1bmx3RXMzU1YtMlpudTNDWERSRnYxMXVJQkgwODZ3WWhrVQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=YnK5IFMrc6Q","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":166,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CL8BEM2rARgBIhMIqMjUi7jrkwMVhKMrBh1-gxMBSKTnrZmFpK65YsoBBP-JbFQ=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbDVGT25OcDl5ZjRRWDNGZ1ViTm5TbkpfMGZYZ3xBQ3Jtc0trckRnYnpOcXA2dWhhcGpTc092Wk10VWpyUG1PM3d1SG5NQnRISUlJSlVwdTNYMmwzVjhIcS1CZG04c0RpQ3EzU0F5ektTUVBuVUkyUWVLT0FISE5GV1pHcFVKczRXbWt6